│── LICENSE
│── .gitignore
└── screenshots/
```

---

# 📚 Modules

### 📊 Dashboard
Displays an overview of the application and student statistics.

### 👨‍🎓 Student Management
Add, edit, delete, and manage student information.

### 📋 Student Records
Displays all registered students in a responsive table.

### 🔍 Search
Quickly search students by ID or Name.

### ✏️ Edit Records
Update student details instantly.

### 🗑️ Delete Records
Remove unwanted student records safely.

---

# 🎯 Objectives

- Develop a responsive web application.
- Perform CRUD operations using JavaScript.
- Practice DOM manipulation.
- Create a clean and modern dashboard.
- Improve front-end development skills.

---

# 🏗 System Architecture

```
User
   │
Web Browser
   │
HTML + CSS Interface
   │
JavaScript Application
   │
Student Data (Array)
   │
Dynamic Dashboard
```

---

# 🗄 Data Structure

### Student Table

| Field | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| Student ID | Unique ID |
| Name | Student Name |
| Email | Student Email |
| Course | Course Name |

---

# 🔄 Project Flow

```
Start
   │
   ▼
Open Dashboard
   │
   ▼
Enter Student Details
   │
   ▼
Click Add Student
   │
   ▼
Display Student Table
   │
   ├── Edit Student
   ├── Delete Student
   └── Search Student
   │
   ▼
End
```

